This file will have all the details of directories and files required for controller node of OpenStack setup.

i) Config :

  a) quantum.conf - This file has to be replaced in the path '/etc/quantum'.
  b) quantum-server - This file has to be replaced in the path '/etc/default'.
  c) quantum-server.conf - This file has to be replaced in the patch '/etc/init'.


   *Note: Create a new directory 'schedulers' in the path '/etc/quantum'.

 d) loadbalancer_scheduler.ini - Copy this file to the path '/etc/quantum/schedulers'.
 e) nwservices_scheduler.ini - Copy this file to the path '/etc/quantum/schedulers'.

